Pipedrive,offers,sales,management,software,focusing,on,increased,sales,and,managing,a,sales,pipeline,The,software,uses,a,drag,and,drop,interface,allowing,users,to,view,the,metrics,making,up,their,sales,pipeline,The,Pipedrive,API,provides,a,RESTful,interface,for,customers,to,integrate,Pipedrive,functions,into,their,own,systems